# Upstream Chromium test: CHECK failure in UpdateKeyDistributionInfo due to
# race condition in async component loading. LoadKeyDistributionData posts
# thread pool tasks and the TestFuture can receive a stale notification.
# No Brave modifications in isolated_web_apps or key_distribution areas.
# 0.7% upstream flake rate over 30 days per LUCI Analysis.
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52733
-IsolatedWebAppUpdateManagerUpdateTest.SkipsUpdateDiscoveryTaskForNotAllowlistedIwa

# Upstream Chromium test: intermittent timing failure in IWA retry logic
# using MOCK_TIME + BackoffEntry. Expected 2 install tasks but got 3 due to
# retry firing earlier than expected. No Brave modifications in IWA policy area.
# Flakes on all platforms (6% upstream flake rate per LUCI Analysis).
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52658
-IsolatedWebAppRetryTest.RetryTriggeredWhenAllTasksDone

# Upstream Chromium test: same IWA retry timing flake. Expected 1 install task
# but got 2 due to retry firing earlier than expected.
# Known upstream flake (8.1% flake rate per LUCI Analysis, 30-day lookback).
# No Brave modifications in IWA policy area.
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52780
-IsolatedWebAppRetryTest.FirstInstallFailsRetrySucceeds

